<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاغْلُظْ عَلَيْهِمْ}</span> ... اسْتَعْمِلِ الخُشُونَةَ وَالشِّدَّةَ فيِ جِهَادِهِمْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَاوَاهُمْ}</span> ... مَسْكَنُهُمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَصِيرُ}</span> ... المَرْجِعُ، وَالمَآلُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَخَانَتَاهُمَا}</span> ... بِالكُفْرِ، وَالمُخَالَفَةِ فِي الدِّينِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلَمْ يُغْنِيَا}</span> ... فَلَمْ يَدْفَعَا وَيَمْنَعَا عَنْهُمَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَحْصَنَتْ}</span> ... حَفِظَتْ وَصَانَتْ عَنِ الزِّنَى.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَنَفَخْنَا فِيهِ مِن رُّوحِنَا}</span> ... جِبْرِيلَ - عليه السلام -، حَيْثُ نَفَخَ فِي جَيْبِ قَمِيصِهَا؛ فَوَصَلَتِ النَّفْخَةُ إِلَى رَحِمِهَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْقَانِتِينَ}</span> ... المُطِيعِينَ لِرَبِّهِمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>